uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e02be385d9ddfd48192d0617d4647f1363be0e00","tid":2278431,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"法庭次次都批准"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"因為根據裁判官條例冇得唔批<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>227章《裁判官條例》<br />\n<br />\n15.律政司司長可藉提出中止檢控而撤回案件<br />\n<br />\n(1)如被控人因可公訴罪行正依據第91、92或92A條在裁判官席前接受審訊，而在判決前的任何階段中，以及在裁判官為裁定應否將被控人交付審判而正在進行的研訊中，<span class=\"red\">律政司司長可將特區擬中止法律程序一事藉書面通知裁判官而提出中止檢控，而被控人隨即須獲撤銷該項中止檢控所關乎的控罪</span>，他如已被押交監獄，須獲釋放，又倘若他正在保釋中，其擔保須予撤銷；但此項對被控人控罪的撤銷並不禁制其後根據相同的事實針對被控人提起法律程序。 <br />\n<br />\n(2)如提出中止檢控時，被控人不在裁判官席前，裁判官書記須隨即將中止檢控一事，安排以書面通知被控人被羈留的監獄的負責人。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"60ae454bbe35798cd97d0a2e96cb6152b41136ea","tid":2278431,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"拜登一勝利宣言 香港好多野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b279260a406828818aaa5e6d8fb3208a2330a533","tid":2278431,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2e5ab20f75fdae3be3efe51b11d7d03d0813f2","tid":2278431,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d180b4d4153f2b9b9329bebdc4348f8f5e72ece2","tid":2278431,"uid":43062,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:07:46.000Z","msg":"仆街啦屌你你老母劣政屍<br />\n<br />\n有哂片有哂醫生報告冇合理定罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla